children.name: JUNE is Trexo’s latest innovation in IP management, built to simplify and accelerate patent and trademark prosecution workflows. By automating critical tasks, JUNE saves time, reduces costs, and ensures unmatched accuracy—helping IP teams work smarter, faster, and more efficiently.
children.characters: JUNE is Trexo’s latest innovation in IP management, built to simplify and accelerate patent and trademark prosecution workflows. By automating critical tasks, JUNE saves time, reduces costs, and ensures unmatched accuracy—helping IP teams work smarter, faster, and more efficiently.

children.name: • Validate: Verify bibliographic details, priority claims, and assignee data with bulk downloads across jurisdictions—minimizing errors. • Generate Documents: Instantly create POA transmittals, 3.73 statements, and Office Action shells—automated from case data and claims. • Search & Download: Bulk-download US & non-US patents with translations, manage IDS references, and auto-calculate USPTO fees. • Standardize: Convert PDFs into USPTO-compliant formats and maintain consistent, accurate IP records.
children.characters:
•	Validate: Verify bibliographic details, priority claims, and assignee data with bulk downloads across jurisdictions—minimizing errors.
•	Generate Documents: Instantly create POA transmittals, 3.73 statements, and Office Action shells—automated from case data and       claims.
•	Search & Download: Bulk-download US & non-US patents with translations, manage IDS references, and auto-calculate USPTO fees.
•	Standardize: Convert PDFs into USPTO-compliant formats and maintain consistent, accurate IP records.
